   <body>
      <p>The error messages are categorized into two types: Static messages and Dynamic messages.</p>
      <p>
         <ul>
            <li>Static messages are standalone messages that have fixed content.</li>
            <li>Dynamic messages have one or more variables that are inserted based on the context from which the message is displayed. These variables can either be a data point from the same form or a related data point from a different form.</li>
         </ul>
      </p>
